title: Roxy Pro France 2013, September 24th - 30th
description:
Following the postponement of the Roxy Pro in Biarritz, the world's top 17 women surfers will, exceptionally, be joining up with their male counterparts for a special meeting of the best surfers on the planet from September 24th! 
 
And so it's a dream line-up expected on the world famous beach breaks of south-west France at the end of the summer... 

We're so excited about this exceptional event coming up that we can't resist to offer you a little taster of what's to come in just a few days time!

LOCATION:
France

ATHLETE: 
Sally Fitzgibbons, Lee-Ann Curren, Stephanie Gilmore, Lisa Andersen, Bianca Buitendag

MUSIC CREDITS
ARTIST: DistantStarr
SONG: Arrive (Instrumental)
